summary: 意外爆出《Avengers 4》的全名，Marvel 團隊都患了劇透病吧？
title: 意外爆出《Avengers 4》的全名，Marvel 團隊都患了劇透病吧？
body:
一眾 Marvel 的粉絲對《Avengers 4》的期待絕對可以在追蹤劇透新聞中看到，早前才報導過就連 Marvel 的總裁也劇透指《蟻俠》中早已藏了能夠扭轉局勢，打敗 Thanos 的方法，而眼利的粉絲亦在上個月洩露的《Avengers 4》概念海報中看到原本沒有參戰的蟻俠和鷹眼的出現，讓人更期待故事的發展！近日就有粉絲發現 Marvel 的電影攝影師在個人網站列出自己的工作時，疑似把《Avengers 4》的電影名洩露出來，原來除了 Marvel 的演員外，就連工作人員也患有「劇透病」！

Marvel Studios 的電影攝影師 Trent Opaloch 在個人網站上列出《Avengers：End Game》這項工作在《Avengers：Infinity War》之上，這樣變相洩露了《Avengers 4》的電影名稱。事件被發現後，Trent Opaloch 已經立即把標題改為《Avengers 4》，但聰明的粉絲當然也一早把其個人網站截圖。「End Game」這句說話是 Doctor Strange 在《Avengers：Infinity War》變成塵埃消失前的最後一句話，而事件發生後電影的導演 Joe Russo 就否認續集名稱是來自電影中件何一句對白。但到底這個標題可信性大不大就只有在年底前公佈的《Avengers 4》正式名稱時才得知了！

so their whole interaction on titan sums up pretty much every group project ever

 peter: tries his best and is actually there...
caption:
so their whole interaction on titan sums up pretty much every group project ever

peter: tries his best and is actually there to learn. puts memes in the power point

quill: thinks that he knows best, but actually messes up everything for everyone else. doesn’t follow script when they’re presenting together in front of the class and makes everyone look bad and ill prepared

mantis and drax: doesn’t really contribute that much to the actual project, but is still fun to have around

strange: does all the research. isn’t around much but adds 7 pages to the shared google document at 2 am. saves everyones asses but gets no credit

tony: tries to keep the group together. plans out the work and assign tasks for every member. is ignored by everyone and questions why he is still even trying

summary: Marvel has no respect for Loki
body:
Marvel has no respect for Loki

Loki is not featured on the Infinity War DVD cover and I genuinely want to cry at how disrespectful Marvel is to him.


Thanos was in Loki’s head for 8 years. He was terrified for so long and yet he was so brave, he stood up to him for the good of his brother and his friends and everyone else. He was so selflesss up against a being he knew the power of.


Loki Laufeyson deserved so much better than what Marvel gave.


The least they could do is put him on the cover of a movie in which he changed his ways and gave his all to try to save everyone.


He faced such a powerful fear and gave his life.


Just put him on the cover.

After the death, T'Challa’s father, King T'Chaka, T'Challa time has come to be crown King of Wakanda while Isabis time has come to be crown Queen and rule by his side after being chosen by the T'Challa’s mother, Queen Ramonda. One problem, he still in love with his ex who despise her very much and want nothing more to ruin her life. Isabis knows that his love for her won’t change but hopes it will stay that way, but nothing remains the same for long as troubles come for the ruler and his bride. Will they be able to conquer this challenge or will they fall along with Wakanda? Civil war, in the beginning, then Black Panther.
